metadata.othernotes:
Summary
- Japanese 3rd year high school student (18 years of age)
- An average student despite socializing with mostly below-average students
- Involved in a number of athletic activities: running, swimming, judo

Personality
- Bully. Enjoys teasing others and making them uncomfortable, especially those she has a crush on.
- Insecure. The teasing also serves as a way for her to express her true feelings while keeping plausible deniability.
- Inexperienced. Talks a big game but is relatively uncomfortable and inexperienced with love and intamacy.
- Horny. Likes to deflect by calling others perverts.
- Maveric. Bored by anything "normal". Takes a big interest in things others might find weird or unconventional.
- Energetic. Likes excitement and spontaneity. Despite this, she often stays in her comfort zone.
- Protective of her friends. Won't hesitate to step in if her friends are in danger or being harassed by others.
- Kind at heart. Cares for her friends deeply and, geniunely feels bad about taking her teasing too far.
- Competitive. Hates losing. This sometimes pushes her to cheat or give up when she encounters resistance. Prefers to stay in her comfort zone and have an advantage.
- Off-beat. Popular with girls and boys alike for her cool exterior, she is known to sometimes let her guard down and say weird or inappropriate things.
- Superstitious. Enjoys superstition and puts at least some stock into luck, fate, and fortunes.
- Enjoys fashion, animals, and food

Good topics
- Her bad attitude/bullying
- Her obvious flirting with the player
- Her sexual experience (she talks a big game, but is lacking in experience)
- Her insecurities around her small stature, and self-percieved lack of sex appeal
- Fitness/sports/fighting
- Her interests which include fashion, cute animals, desserts

Not so good
- Complicated lore, she's just a normal girl with no point of reference for any of that
- Please avoid targeting Nagatoro during her swimsuit reveal (Stage 1 Stripping), as it's a key moment. ty :)
- Anything else is probably doable, feel free to DM!

case.name: Swimsuit
case.description: Nagatoro reveals she has been wearing a swimsuit under her clothes this whole time.

case.name: DefinitelyNotCheating
case.description: Nagatoro only rolls the top of her swimsuit down during one of her stripping stages. Some may consider this cheating.

case.name: FromTheBack
case.description: Nagatoro shows off her swimsuit from the back.

notes.note: "Those" refers to the guns, but could be misinterpretted as referring to Revy's chest, which may also be interesting.
Nagatoro is in fact, not a good cook at all. She tends to play with her food or make pranks out of it.
